summary:
At Utrecht University, I explore interconnected systems and learn to see the Earth from a Physics perspective . Additionally, I have a passion for coding and like to spend my time manipulating and visualizing large datasets.  

I am a joyful and energetic person who enjoys rolling up his sleeves. However, I am evaluative in my character and calm in my emotions.  

For more information, my CV and examples of what I can do for you and your company, have a look at my website: timomillenaar.nl (clickable link in contact information).
